text: Xiangyang Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Longcheng District, Chaoyang, Liaoning, China. , it has 4 residential communities under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Liaoning == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Liaoning Category:Chaoyang, Liaoning
